912     * @return OrderImport
913     */
914    public OrderImport build() {
915        Objects.requireNonNull(orderNumber, OrderImport.class + ": orderNumber is missing");
916        Objects.requireNonNull(totalPrice, OrderImport.class + ": totalPrice is missing");
917        return new OrderImportImpl(orderNumber, customer, customerEmail, lineItems, customLineItems, totalPrice,
918            taxedPrice, shippingAddress, billingAddress, customerGroup, country, orderState, shipmentState,
919            paymentState, shippingInfo, completedAt, custom, inventoryMode, taxRoundingMode, taxCalculationMode, origin,
920            itemShippingAddresses, store, state);
921    }

942    /**
943     * create builder for OrderImport instance
944     * @param template instance with prefilled values for the builder
945     * @return builder
946     */
947    public static OrderImportBuilder of(final OrderImport template) {
948        OrderImportBuilder builder = new OrderImportBuilder();
949        builder.orderNumber = template.getOrderNumber();
950        builder.customer = template.getCustomer();
951        builder.customerEmail = template.getCustomerEmail();
952        builder.lineItems = template.getLineItems();
953        builder.customLineItems = template.getCustomLineItems();
954        builder.totalPrice = template.getTotalPrice();
955        builder.taxedPrice = template.getTaxedPrice();
956        builder.shippingAddress = template.getShippingAddress();
957        builder.billingAddress = template.getBillingAddress();
958        builder.customerGroup = template.getCustomerGroup();
959        builder.country = template.getCountry();
960        builder.orderState = template.getOrderState();
961        builder.shipmentState = template.getShipmentState();
962        builder.paymentState = template.getPaymentState();
963        builder.shippingInfo = template.getShippingInfo();
964        builder.completedAt = template.getCompletedAt();
965        builder.custom = template.getCustom();
966        builder.inventoryMode = template.getInventoryMode();
967        builder.taxRoundingMode = template.getTaxRoundingMode();
968        builder.taxCalculationMode = template.getTaxCalculationMode();
969        builder.origin = template.getOrigin();
